name: No Queue Culture
description:
No Queue Culture

The arcade game where you don't care about speed limits or traffic queues! Hurry through the roads to get to different destinations before anyone else. E.g. the local pizzeria that is giving free margheritas to the first 25 customers, or your grandma's house because you forgot her birthday. You could also just try to get as far as possible in the endless mode.

Current version: 0.1
